<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to the MHDT Connect App, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      Your user account was just created, allowing you to log in to the
      <%= link_to 'Mars Hill Downtown Connect App', home_url %>. Your username and temporary password are shown below;
      when you first log in, you will be required to change your password. (You may also change your username, if you
      like...go to "My Profile" after logging in.)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>Username:</b> <pre><%= @user.username %></pre><br />
      <b>Password:</b> <pre><%= @password %></pre><br />
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any difficulty logging in, please contact <%= mail_to 'The Webmaster', webmaster_email %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Sincerely,<br />
      The Webmaster (a.k.a., Ryan Saunders)
    </p>
  </body>
</html>

